<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Game of Life</title>
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #121212;
          color: white;
          text-align: center;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: center;
          height: 130vh;
      }
      .container {
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 10px;
          box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 800px;
          overflow-y: auto; /* Rende il contenuto scorrevole */
          height: 100vh; /* Imposta un'altezza fissa per il container */
      }
      h1 {
          font-size: 3rem;
          margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      p {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          line-height: 1.5;
      }
      p strong {
          font-size: 1.3rem;
          color: #ff6600;
      }
      .btn {
          background: #ff6600;
          color: white;
          padding: 10px 20px;
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          transition: 0.3s;
          display: inline-block;
          margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .btn:hover {
          background: #cc5200;
      }
      .btn-back {
          background-color: #444;
      }
      .game-output {
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 10px;
          margin-top: 10px;
          width: auto;
          min-width: 300px;  /* Impedisce che diventi troppo piccolo */
          max-width: 90vw;   /* Evita di superare lo schermo */
          text-align: center;
          display: inline-block; /* Adatta il contenitore al contenuto */
          box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .game-output pre {
          font-family: monospace;
          font-size: 1.3rem;
          white-space: pre-wrap;
          word-wrap: break-word;
          background: black;
          padding: 15px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          color: #00ff00;
          margin: 0 auto;
          display: inline-block;
          max-height: 60vh;  /* Evita che diventi pi√π grande dello schermo */
          overflow: auto;  /* Abilita lo scroll solo se necessario */
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Sei pronto?</h1>
  <p>Mettiti comodo e goditi la generazione del Gioco della Vita secondo le tue regole.</p>

  <div id="game-output" class="game-output">
    <h2>File Caricato</h2>
    <pre><%= @game_of_life_file %></pre>
  </div>

  <%= button_to 'Avvia la generazione', generate_game_path(@game), id: 'start-game', method: :post, class: 'btn' %>
</div>

<%= button_to 'Logout', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: 'btn' %>
<p><a href="<%= root_path %>" class="btn btn-back">Torna alla Home</a></p>
</body>
</html>
